title: Panasonic 5-Blade Shaver LV Series - Experience the multi-flex 3D head (English)
description:
The new Multi-Flex 3D Head hugs your face, staying in close contact with your skin. Also smooth Slider glides smoothly over the skin for an even gentler shave.
Experience a new way to shave.
